FBIS3-54157 "drnes015_s_94001" FBIS-NES-94-015 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 Iran President Sends Condolences to Syria's al-Asad LD2201115394 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 1030 GMT 22 Jan 94 LD2201115394 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Language: Persian Article Type:BFN [Text] President Hashemi-Rafsanjani issued a message of condolence today following the death of the Syrian president's son. The message expresses sympathy and sorrow about the sad incident, and asks God Almighty to grant forgiveness to the deceased son of Hafiz al-Asad and patience and endurance to the grieving families.
